textBeforeTable: ALABAMA Below is the full list of the 2014 Choice Hotels International Platinum Hospitality Award Winners across the United States: For more information or to make your reservation at any one of these award-winning hotels visit www.ChoiceHotels.com or call the Choice Hotels toll-free reservation line at 1-800-4CHOICE. As top performing properties operating under the Choice Hotels flag, these Platinum-graded hotels have risen to the highest tiers among the company's portfolio of 10 brands and the Ascend Hotel Collection for having demonstrated an extraordinary focus on lodging excellence. Platinum honorees are rated in the top 3% of their respective brands based on guest satisfaction scores for superior customer service, property condition and cleanliness. Additional award criteria are evaluated by Choice Hotels through its official property ranking reports. "These hotel owners and operators demonstrate an extraordinary commitment to excellence and outstanding guest service which have earned them this Platinum distinction as one of the best hotels among their respective brands," said Stephen P. Joyce, president and chief executive officer for Choice Hotels. "We here at Choice Hotels International are proud to partner with them because they represent the foundation upon which the company was built: providing an exceptional guest experience."
